{"id":34466,"date":"2020-10-14T15:00:27","date_gmt":"2020-10-14T11:00:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=34466"},"modified":"2020-10-14T15:01:25","modified_gmt":"2020-10-14T11:01:25","slug":"two-men-share-lineage-asabiyyah","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/14\/two-men-share-lineage-asabiyyah\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Tribalism: Two men share lineage, one man goes to Hellfire"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Two men shared their lineages in the time of Moses, upon him be peace. One man boasted to the other: I am this person, son of this person, back for nine generations. Who are you? You have no mother? The other man said: I am this person, son of this person, son of Islam. Allah revealed to Moses in regards to these two who shared their lineages: As for you tribalist, you shared lineage back for nine generations in Hellfire and you are the tenth of them. As for you, you shared lineage back for two generations in Paradise and you are the third of them.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 21178<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e <strong>\u0627\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0628\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0639\u064e\u0647\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0645\u0